#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "YAML configuration"
msgstr "YAML 配置"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can use a YAML file,`application.yaml`, to configure your {project-name} application instead of the standard Java properties file, `application.properties`."
msgstr "您可以使用 YAML 文件 `application.yaml` 来配置您的 {project-name} 应用程序，而不是使用标准的 Java 属性文件 `application.properties` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "link:https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YAML[YAML] is widely used for defining resource descriptors, especially in Kubernetes."
msgstr "link:https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YAML[YAML] 被广泛用于定义资源描述符，特别是在 Kubernetes 中。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Enable YAML configuration"
msgstr "启用 YAML 配置"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To enable YAML configuration, add the `quarkus-config-yaml` extension:"
msgstr "要启用 YAML 配置，请添加 `quarkus-config-yaml` 扩展："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Alternatively, add the following dependency to your project:"
msgstr "或者，将以下依赖项添加到你的项目中："

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "pom.xml"
msgstr "pom.xml"

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "build.gradle"
msgstr "build.gradle"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"After adding the extension or dependency, to avoid confusion, remove the `src/main/resources/application.properties`\n"
"file and create a `src/main/resources/application.yaml` file."
msgstr "添加扩展或依赖后，为避免混淆，请删除 `src/main/resources/application.properties` 文件，并创建一个 `src/main/resources/application.yaml` 文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If both files are present, {project-name} gives precedence to properties in the YAML file."
msgstr "如果这两个文件都存在，{project-name} 会优先采用 YAML 文件中的属性。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"{project-name} recognizes both `.yaml` and `.yml` file extensions. If both files are available, {project-name}\n"
"gives precedence to the `.yaml` file and then the `.yml` file."
msgstr "{project-name} 同时支持 `.yaml` 和 `.yml` 文件扩展名。如果两种文件都存在，{project-name} 会优先处理 `.yaml` 文件，其次是 `.yml` 文件。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Example YAML configurations"
msgstr "YAML 配置示例"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The following snippets give examples of YAML configurations:"
msgstr "以下代码片段展示了 YAML 配置的示例："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can also use JSON in the YAML file to describe the configuration. Use a single format per file. The file extension\n"
"is either `yaml` or `yml`."
msgstr "您也可以在 YAML 文件中使用 JSON 来描述配置。每个文件请使用一种格式。文件扩展名应为 `yaml` 或 `yml` 。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Profiles"
msgstr "个人资料"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "As you can see in the previous snippet, you can use xref:config-reference.adoc#profiles[profiles] in YAML."
msgstr "如前面的代码片段所示，您可以在 YAML 中使用 xref:config-reference.adoc#profiles[配置文件] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In YAML, keys that begin with `%` are not allowed.\n"
"However, profile keys must start with this symbol.\n"
"To resolve this, enclose the profile keys in double quotes, as demonstrated by the example, `\"%test\"`."
msgstr "在 YAML 中，不允许键以 `%` 开头。但是，配置键必须以此符号开头。为了解决这个问题，请将配置键用双引号括起来，如示例 `“%test”` 所示。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"All configurations under the `\"%test\"` key activate only when the `test` profile is enabled.\n"
"For instance, the previous snippet shows that OpenID Connect (OIDC) (`quarkus.oidc.enabled: false`) is disabled when the `test` profile is active.\n"
"Without the `test` profile, OIDC is enabled by default."
msgstr "`“%test”` 键下的所有配置仅在 `测试` 配置文件启用时生效。例如，前面的代码片段显示，当 `测试` 配置文件处于活动状态时，OpenID Connect（OIDC）（ `quarkus.oidc.enabled: false` ）会被禁用。如果未启用 `测试` 配置文件，OIDC 默认处于启用状态。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can also define custom profiles, such as `%staging` in the following example:"
msgstr "您还可以定义自定义配置文件，例如以下示例中的 `%staging` ："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you enable the `staging` profile, the HTTP port is set to `8082` instead of `8081`."
msgstr "如果启用了 `测试环境` 配置文件，HTTP 端口将设置为 `8082` ，而不是 `8081` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The YAML configuration also supports profile-aware files.\n"
"In this case, properties for a specific profile can reside in an `application-{profile}.yaml` named file.\n"
"The previous example can be expressed as:"
msgstr "YAML 配置还支持基于配置文件的文件。在这种情况下，特定配置文件的属性可以放在名为 `application-{profile}.yaml` 的文件中。前面的示例可以表示为："

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "application-staging.yaml"
msgstr "application-staging.yaml"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"An `application.yaml` file must exist (even if empty) in the exact location of the profile-aware\n"
"(`application-{profile}.yaml`) file to be included in the configuration to ensure a consistent order when\n"
"loading the files. All profile files must match the same extension of the main file."
msgstr "必须在配置中包含的“支持配置文件”（ `application-{profile}.yaml` ）文件的确切位置存在一个 `application.yaml` 文件（即使为空），以确保加载文件时的顺序保持一致。所有配置文件必须与主文件具有相同的扩展名。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Expressions"
msgstr "表达式"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The YAML format also supports xref:config-reference.adoc#property-expressions[property expressions], by using the same format as Java properties:"
msgstr "YAML 格式还支持 xref:config-reference.adoc#property-expressions[属性表达式] ，其格式与 Java 属性相同："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can reference nested properties by using the `.` (dot) separator, as in `${x.factor}`."
msgstr "您可以使用 `.` （点）分隔符来引用嵌套属性，例如 `${x.factor}` 。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "External application.yaml file"
msgstr "外部 application.yaml 文件"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `application.yaml` file can also be placed in `config/application.yaml` to specialize the runtime configuration.\n"
"The file must be present in the root of the working directory relative to the {project-name} application runner:"
msgstr "`application.yaml` 文件也可以放置在 `config/application.yaml` 中，以实现运行时配置的定制化。该文件必须位于相对于 {project-name} 应用程序运行器的作业目录根目录下："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The values from this file override any values from the regular `application.yaml` file if it exists."
msgstr "如果存在常规的 `application.yaml` 文件，则此文件中的值将覆盖该文件中的任何值。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Configuration property conflicts"
msgstr "配置属性冲突"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The MicroProfile Config specification defines configuration properties as an arbitrary `.`-delimited string.\n"
"However, structured formats such as YAML only support a subset of the possible configuration namespace.\n"
"For example, consider the two configuration properties `one.two` and `one.two.three`.\n"
"One property is the prefix of another, so it might not be immediately evident how to specify both keys in your YAML configuration."
msgstr "MicroProfile Config 规范将配置属性定义为 `以点（.）` 分隔的任意字符串 `。` 然而，诸如 YAML 之类的结构化格式仅支持配置命名空间中的一部分。例如，考虑两个配置属性 `one.two` 和 `one.two.three` 。 其中一个属性是另一个属性的前缀，因此可能无法立即明确在 YAML 配置中如何同时指定这两个键。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This is solved by using `~` as a `null` key to represent any YAML property that is a prefix of another one:"
msgstr "通过将 `~` 作为 `空` 键来表示作为另一个 YAML 属性前缀的任何 YAML 属性，即可解决此问题："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/config-yaml.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "YAML `null` keys are not included in the assembly of the configuration property name, allowing them to be used at any level for disambiguating configuration properties."
msgstr "YAML `中的空键` 不会被纳入配置属性名称的构建过程，因此可以在任何层级使用它们来消除配置属性的歧义。"
